Stockholm, Sweden
About Nonius



Nonius provides the ultimate Cloud Guest Technology, offering a green, lean and efficient Cloud Solutions Portfolio to elevate the digital guest experience and streamline hotel operations. Our suite includes Mobile App, Cast, Interactive TV, Guest Wi-Fi, Networks, Digital Signage, Voice, and seamless Integrations with other hotel systems. Trusted worldwide, Nonius serves over 574,000 rooms across diverse markets, including hotels, apartments, co-living spaces, healthcare, maritime, and sport and leisure facilities.



Job Description


We are seeking a professional to join our team as a Field Service Technician. In this role, you will collaborate closely with the Subsidiary Director as part of an international team.  

This position is based at our Stockholm office.


Responsibilities


* Within the scope of execution of tasks of Projects / Field Customer Support:
* + Installation / Replacement of Telecommunications, Electrical and Multimedia equipment (Routers, Switches, Access points, UPS, TVs, STBs, cameras);
	+ Perform task / worksheets of surveys to structured networks and wifi; Perform task / worksheets for installation / correction of customer network racks;
	+ Perform task / worksheets for installation / correction and alignment of satellite antennas;
	+ Perform task / worksheets of installation / electrical correction in Racks (UPS, cables, etc.).
* Projects:
* + Responsibility for deliver small complexity projects with high customer satisfaction;
	+ Execute project tasks for the deployment of Nonius solutions;
	+ Lease with other Engineers and or Technicians.
* Customer Support / Field Support:
* + Attend sites to resolve issues related with Nonius Solutions at our customers;
	+ Install, upgrade and maintain equipment under SLA;
	+ Provide a high level of customer care within the terms of the SLAs;
	+ Timely completion of all paperwork related to the site visits;
	+ Liaise with senior engineers, management, contractors and customers;
	+ Provide remote technical support to existing customer sites;
	+ Ensure all work is completed to a high standard and to agreed processes.
* Sales Engineering Support:
* + Do site visits/surveys to address customer requirements to quote Nonius solutions;
	+ Lease with Sales Team and Managing Director when needed to address specific customer requirements / sales opportunities;
	+ Assist the Subsidiary sales team solutions presentations to customers.

Must Have


* We are looking for a smart and good spirit person;
* High school diploma or equivalent, along with a 2 year technical degree or equivalent work experience in Telecom and/or Networking;
* Ability to work in WAN/LAN environment;
* Working with routers, servers and TCP/IP environment;
* CCNA or other switching/routing courses or work experience that can be considered equivalent;
* Valid driver’s license and be available to travel within the country and abroad;
* Ability to meet deadlines and work independently;
* Must have excellent communication skills and outstanding customer awareness skills;
* Fluent in Swedish;
* Fluent in English.
Nice to Have


* Experience with Hotels, TV systems, Coax and IP networks, Wi-Fi, IT, ISP;
* Hospitality experience, preferably Hotel IT or vendor;
* Linux admin experience and shell scripting;
* Awareness of hotel chain brand standards.

What's great in the job?





* Great team of smart people, in a friendly and open culture
* Real responsibilities and autonomy
* Expand your knowledge of various countries and regions
* Great career opportunity in a fast-evolving Technology company
* Contribute to the greater experience of millions of Travellers around the World!
